11:10.540 --> 11:11.830
♪ I got money now ♪

11:11.830 --> 11:13.830
♪ All I really understand is ♪

11:13.830 --> 11:15.460
♪ Since that check came in ♪

11:15.460 --> 11:18.670
♪ Everybody's talkin' like
